{"tid":505723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人向黃毓民集體道歉 + 請求參加九西補選救港大聯署","createTime":"2017-12-21T12:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T09:12:06.000Z","uid":76115,"like":15,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a976020689dd0aa2c51b49fbde6b1ddb2d633604","tid":505723,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"睇左呢個月毓民踩場對飯民應付議事規則嘅批判<br />\n<br />\n我敢講毓民係唯一知道而家香港每一步exactly應該點行嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毓民落選, 所有香港人除左欠佢一句&quot;對唔住&quot;之外, 其實亦都欠自己一句對唔住, 因為係我地放棄毓民, 自己將香港搞成而家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毓民今年已經六十六歲, 隨時都會死, 所以今次九西補選真係香港人最後一次贖罪、最後一次救自己嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與其含撚投泛民, 不如盡一分力集氣請求毓民重返議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聯署人:<br />\n1. 社會主義者佛利民"},{"pid":"2af1e9bf65599716c59a8eb74d696ddf0201e00d","tid":505723,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"毓民議會勇武事蹟回顧<br />\n<br />\n「創科局」黃毓民當著陳健波的面打爛銘牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hK0QYzKnPTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhK0QYzKnPTM&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=eed42397\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hK0QYzKnPTM</a><br />\n<br />\n毓民發火　財會上拍主席台爆缸<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0aGa-CwqzI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Df0aGa-CwqzI&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=77cb43d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f0aGa-CwqzI</a>"},{"pid":"4dc69ab03ec27b0f70b4efa96823fc76549df16f","tid":505723,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p